title: Novo Nordisk says it will take legal action after Hims & Hers reveals $49 copy of Wegovy pill
summary_full: Hims said it would sell a copy of the newly launched weight loss pill for $49, far less than the $149 Novo sells the branded pill for.
summary_public: Hims said it would sell a copy of the newly launched weight loss pill for $49, far less than the $149 Novo sells the branded pill for.
